title: #105: The Moon Landing with Agostino Zoida
description: Thank you for tuning into for another episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli.  This episode the guys welcome from the Homeschooled podcast, Agostino Zoida, to discuss all the interesting stuff about the Moon landing. Thank you for tuning in and supporting the show.
